Recipe: Fresh Tomato Basil Pasta with Ricotta
Servings: 4

Ingredients:
12 oz pasta (any shape)
2 Tbsp olive oil
2 cloves garlic
2 pints grape tomatoes
1 Tbsp butter
1/2 cup fresh basil, loosely packed
1/2 cup whole milk ricotta
salt & pepper to taste

